+rg353m_model_matches_seed() {
+  # RG353M boots through ROCKNIX's RG353P-family DTB, so /proc/device-tree/model
+  # can report either the physical RG353M name or the RG353P DTB name. Accept
+  # the narrower Android/RK817 RG353M seed only when the SD-compatible pair is
